-- Gold Reverses Earlier Gains to Near Record, Retreating in London, New York
-- John Deane
-- 2010-06-28T14:51:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/gold-reverses-earlier-gains-to-near-record-retreating-in-london-new-york.html

          
          
             Gold for immediate delivery reversed
earlier gains to decline 0.3 percent to $1,251.45 an ounce in
London trading at 3:48 p.m. local time. Gold futures in New York
fell 0.4 percent to $1,251.30 an ounce.  
          
          


  


        